profile_positions.description:
Cristal is an ice cream and fast-food store and factory, specializing in artisan and high-standard of ice creams.

• Administrative Management, maintaining the company in accordance with quality and safety, regulating standards and programs. Responsible to manage a team of 15 sellers and attendants;
• Responsible for managing a company's overall operations, driving profitability, managing company organizational structure, strategy, and communicating with the board. 
•Identify and assess customers’ needs to achieve satisfaction, also build sustainable relationships and trust with customer accounts through open and interactive communication;

Achievements:
• Improved Customer Experience and exceeding their expectations by taking different actions through new events, adding different flavors on the menu, creating promotions, and adopting a data-led strategy to evaluate the customer base and implement methods to drive customer growth;
• Also improved the internal customer experience by driving a safer environment through risk assessment, prevention, and mitigation. As well as addressed quality and safety training to employees;
• Headed an audit annual calendar,
• Increased sales by 58% in a period of 12 months, enabling the opening of two new stores in strategic neighborhoods of the city.
• I actively spearheaded a project aimed at reducing environmental impacts by 67% related to the utilization of disposable cups and pots, while also significantly cutting packaging expenses. Through my management of the 6 Sigma project, I successfully increased the adoption of reusable cups and pots in Cristal's stores, resulting in a 25% profit savings for the company.

Living for 4 years in the USA had the opportunity to learn English and Spanish, working and studying in Miami. I could increase my multicultural international professional experience. 

Working in American Uni - a Bag and Luggage Manufactory American company, my activities were:

-General management assistance, 
-Develop market analysis through data collection and KPIs control to develop new product delivery routes, anticipating sales and exceeding customer expectations;
-Increase sales due to my resourceful multilingual skills;
-Attract new customers and experience customer service abilities.

volunteer_experiences.description:
Praia Mar Community Association, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil
Member of the PraiaMar community, friends of the environment project. The project aims to increase people's environmental awareness in the care of the fauna and flora of the community. Distribution of folders and explanatory booklets, development of ecological walks for cleaning the beach and the neighborhood.
• Developing projects directly with the community president for environmental preservation actions; 
• Maintaining cleanliness and order in the neighborhood; 
• Implement the selective garbage collection center; 
• Developing awareness of the local population for the correct segregation of domestic waste for recycling.
